Provisioning staff
From backend/:

npm run provision-staff -- admin you@company.com YourSecurePass "Your Name"
or manager instead of admin. Uses MONGODB_URI from .env.

Shared helper
utils/roles.js exports isStaff, canEditListing, and role sets used by auth and controllers.

